<Verbatim PAsource="" >Metropolitan Police Sgt Mark Workman said Pc Joy Hendricks, 35, punched him and hit him with the cue as they waited to go on a drugs raid.
</Verbatim>

<Rewrite PAsource="" >But </Rewrite>
